&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/Tibor17/junit5-mockito-examples&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/Tibor17/junit5-mockito-examples&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

